1. TP to lever → pull lever (fireclickdetector + Levers_RequestPull)
2. Fire Raids_BossChallenge(bossIdx) → opens door
3. Fire Raids_StartBoss(bossIdx) → spawns boss
4. Burst tap kills boss instantly (one-shot)
5. Boss completed

Boss1: after room 3 (RequiredRoom=3), pos (-82,108,-5941)
Boss2: after room 9 (RequiredRoom=9), pos (833,108,-6009)  
Boss3: after completion (RequiredRoom=10+completed), pos (1146,113,-5438)
  - Boss3 Mythic requires difficulty 45000 (we run at 50000!)

Difficulty 50000 (server doesn't validate)
LeprechaunChest added
Burst default 1x
]]

